AI Engineer Roadmap\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 AI engineering is the process of building systems that can learn from data, make predictions, generate content, and automate decision-making. An AI engineer works with machine learning models, deep learning systems, data pipelines, and modern AI tools like large language models.\
This roadmap takes a beginner from programming basics to building and deploying real-world AI systems.\
